'''Primary Shaping''' was the educational system for the [[Shaper caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. In this system, crechelings would be instructed on the various aspects of the [[Shaping protocol]]s. The dormitories of the young Shapers were guarded by [[Warrior]]s.

